{
  "stem": "2684.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which meant that I became a dishwasher, washing up the floors after, and he started cooking for about 3,000-4,000 people, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a huge kitchen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of people worked there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to me he didn't let me eat the heavy food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because after the typhus, he cooked me soups, especially broth-- what you would call broth, we call it [NON-ENGLISH] Light stuff which I started slowly eating and started gaining my-- not energy, my weight-- and my system started getting used to food.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from then on after, I don't know, two , three weeks later, all I seen in the hall was fire.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody was cooking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because the chef what was making was very nice, but everybody was cooking the menu what we've talked about in the lager.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had the bean soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had the-- I had a Berliner with the eggs on the middle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't have, unfortunately, poppy seeds, so I couldn't eat poppy seed noodle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I stayed and ate so many eggs and Berliner you have no idea.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that went on, and went on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and then the strength started coming back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then we took a train and we went into Munich.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in Munich, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it was to us like Shangri-La.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean, it was something we never seen before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But before we went to Munich, we explored the surrounding of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the farmers there, we went-- we cut down a piece of cloth from the depot and exchanged it for the piece of speck, or a piece of salami, or a piece of meat, or flour, or so forth.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That's how we could cook.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And nobody knew anything about what happened to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
